Faster upload speed that was before 1.7.0, to check it you can run the previous code with 1.6.8 or use https://codesandbox.io/p/sandbox/axios-fast-progress-1-6-8-rw7vdd?workspaceId=0994da35-60c6-4b2e-af43-fa484a57a293. You should see something similar to `Finished uploading file, axios made 6.2 progress reports per second`.

